Goal: 
1. Design a sign up page that greets the user and ask for relevant details. 
2. Validate it and show it in the browser with JSON pattern. 
3. Deploy this app in the cloud. 
4. Deploy this app behind load balancer and run it in two VMs

Steps:
Deploy the signuppage app on my VM:
1. Switch to root sudo su – 
2. Enter command for update and install:
apt-get update
apt-get install apache2
apt-get install php
3. Go to external IP in browser to check whether apache works
	http://external IP
4. Enter cd /var/www/html
5. Create signuppage.html vi signuppage.html 

Finally, search http://external IP/signuppage.html for result and test.
